them or their safety. A pretty funny situation when you think about it and something we can all relate to.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Community</h2>Want to find out more about UnderMine? Ask us questions? Post dumb pictures? Join our Discord!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/656350/extras/f1a14a246aca3997d6b1dcf1bc71d84e.avif?t=1724975181\" width=600 height=100 /></span>",
